  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "TC3XX has an separate controller which runs with XC800 Core which is used to wakeup the Tricore controller"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Below is the diagram which shows the shared pins between Tricore and SCR"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Note : Only these pins can wake the Tricore on entering standby mode"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "SCR need an separate Compiler to compile its code Keil C51 (This compiler can be downloaded from VP_ArtifactoryTools Antifactory)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Cerberus PF team has an PoC for waking Tricore with SCR, below is the link"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Integration of SCR in Cerberus PF - XC-CT Cerberus Platform - Docupedia (bosch.com)"
